data.description: With a BRAND NEW HVAC system and fresh paint inside, this LOVELY Davis Hills five-bedroom home is now available, and it has SO MUCH to offer!! Convenient to the hospital, downtown Thomaston, and the schools, this home is in the PERFECT in-town location while still having space to spread out on the HUGE corner lot. The tall ceilings and beautiful brick fireplace in the living room create the most amazing ambiance right when you walk in the front door. The STUNNING kitchen has been upgraded with a GORGEOUS tile backsplash and stainless-steel appliances. Two beautiful sunrooms offer even more space; one sunroom is currently being used as a cozy breakfast room, the other sunroom is currently a convenient bar and an extension of the large living room. The beautiful separate dining room features new, modern lighting and beautiful molding. The split floor plan is perfect for families or for guests offering privacy while still keeping everyone all on one floor. The HUGE owner's suite features large, double closets and a recently renovated owner's bathroom with a new tile shower, separate soaking tub, and double vanity. There are four more bedrooms, two of which have been recently painted and feature new, modern lighting. With four sides brick, LOTS of upgrades, and a fenced backyard in one of Thomaston's most prestigious neighborhoods, this move-in ready home has all you've been looking for and SO MUCH MORE!
